{"tid":180450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"本港2月私樓售價指數再創新高　連升11個月","createTime":"2017-03-31T02:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T02:41:27.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de31178180738ed075d15f4ad97d008165de57a6","tid":180450,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"本港私人住宅樓價連續4個月創新高。<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署數據顯示，2月私樓售價指數升至312.8，按月升近1.1%，連升11個月，升幅較1月的0.7%擴大。<br />\n<br />\n2月私樓售價指數按年亦升14.3%，今年首兩個月樓價累計升近1.8%。<br />\n<br />\n期內，中小型單位樓價按月升幅擴大至1.1%，按年亦升14.5%。大型單位樓價按月升幅則收窄約0.3%，按年升8.8%。<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1322677-20170331.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1322677-20170331.htm&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3b50aa20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1322677-20170331.htm&h=34a9e75b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1322677-20170331.htm</a>"}]}